0.0.2.2: 12/19/2004

	* Fixed build process on AMD64 (casting issues in libmelf)
	* Fixed minor memory leaks under certain conditions in verification
	
0.0.2.1: 06/05/2004

	* Fixed build process on AMD64

0.0.2.0: 05/04/2004

	* Improvements to the signature algorithm
	  * Signature versioning now supported
	  * Checksums include section headers, program headers, and the elf
	    header, and of course their respective contents.
   * Code clean up
	* Changed the licensing scheme to the ``Artistic License''
